      • getAverageByCourse

        private int getAverageByCourse(Course course)
        Gets the overall average of a course that the person is enrolled in or teaching.
        Parameters:
        course - The course that the person is enrolled in or teaching.
        Returns:
        The overall average that the person has in the course (if it's a student, returns the student's mark in that course, if it's a teacher, returns the average of all the student's marks in that course).

      • getOverallAverage

        int getOverallAverage()
        Gets the overall average of the person. If it's a teacher, returns the average of all his/her course averages. It it's a student, returns the average of all their marks in each course.
        Returns:
        The overall average of the person.

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Person person)
        Compares two people by username.
        Returns:
        A negative number if the person's username is less lexicographically than the given person's username, zero if they are the same, and a positive number if the person's username is lexicographically greater than the given person's username.
